UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind, United Nations Working Together. title.narrative: New Element

description.narrative: UNICEF continued to work with the Government at federal and FMS level to develop, review and advocate for policies, legislations, and structures mainly in the area of child rights, child justice and Civil Registration and Vital Statistics ;particularly birth registration. Moreover, UNICEF continued to support thecapacity enhancement and professionalization of the social service workforce and in CP/GBV service provision through the social work degree and diploma program and case management roll out.However little progress was made on the legislative front, particularly on the Child Rights Bill where significant amendments inconsistent with the UNCRC were introduced in early 2021 | Status:Met | As-of Date:06/01/2022
